<item>
            <title>[PIG-4948] Pig on Tez AM use too much memory on a small cluster</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4948</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig will use 1024M for AM memory even if &quot;tez.am.resource.memory.mb&quot; is smaller. On a small cluster such as sandbox, the total memory is very small (eg, 2g) and this will make the capacity full and not able to run any job.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
