                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15378576" author="daijy" created="Thu, 14 Jul 2016 23:16:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am going to introduce an option to respect tez.am.resource.memory.mb, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rohini&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rohini&quot;&gt;rohini&lt;/a&gt;, do you have any different opinion?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15383411" author="rohini" created="Tue, 19 Jul 2016 01:02:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Could you rename it to pig.tez.configure.am.memory or pig.tez.autoconfigure.am.memory ? Also could you make the constant name also same so that we keep naming convention consistent like in TezConfiguration. i.e PIG_TEZ_CONFIGURE_AM_MEMORY . Unrelated, I noticed that ENABLE_ATS does not confirm to that. Could you change that as well to PIG_ATS_ENABLED? If you want to retain existing one for backward compatibility with 0.15, you can move it to deprecated section below.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15383439" author="daijy" created="Tue, 19 Jul 2016 01:23:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rename pig.tez.override.am.memory to pig.tez.configure.am.memory as suggested. For PIG_ATS_ENABLED change, created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4951&quot; title=&quot;Rename PIG_ATS_ENABLED constant&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4951&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-4951&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15383441" author="rohini" created="Tue, 19 Jul 2016 01:24:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15383445" author="daijy" created="Tue, 19 Jul 2016 01:29:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to both 0.16 branch and trunk. Thanks Rohini for review!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15393711" author="rohini" created="Tue, 26 Jul 2016 12:21:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4962&quot; title=&quot;Estimate smaller Tez AM memory for smaller count of tasks&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4962&quot;&gt;PIG-4962&lt;/a&gt; to estimate smaller heap for small jobs with fewer tasks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
